    # Folder size (compressed): 286451492 bytes / 290 MB (megabytes) / 276.6 MiB (mebibytes)
    # Compression savings: 72.7%
    # Approximate total folder size (files + file overhead + folder overhead): 293218773 bytes / 293.2 MB (megabytes) / 279.6 MiB (mebibytes)
